<br>
Escape: no offense we got the shaft here. it should be 3 skill levels, 3 points each maybe, and the timer should decrease 72, 36, 18. Keep in mind if this is absolutly identical to feign death, that we are only hidden after we use it, unlike monks who are feigned. So even if we completly wipe agro, the mob is just going to reaggro us if we are near to it and our 72 minutes is down the toilet.<br>
